						<summary>

						<p>On a boulder near the <hi rend="italic">doṇi</hi> on the hill.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1076 A.D.</hi> </p>						

						<p>This very much damaged record, registers a grant of land by an individual whose name is lost. It mentions <hi rend="italic">perggaḍe</hi> Māramayya and the administrative division Mosaḷikal-300.</p>						

						<p>There is a mention of <hi rend="italic">piriya-kōlu</hi> the measuring rod. It is dated Śaka 998, Naḷa, Pushya, Śu. 3 corresponding to 1076 A.D., December 1, Thursday.</p>						

						</summary>
