<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samadhigatapaṁcamahā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>māhmātī puravarēśvara <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> sakavarṣa 998 neya naḷa saṁvatsarada puṣya suddha 3 <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> perggaḍe māramayyanu perggaḍe <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ḷayyanu samasta parigrahamiṟe mosaḷikalmūnūṟaṁ
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> brāhmaṇara mane Ayyaṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> (vo)ladalli taḷavṛttiyāgi sarvanamasyamāgi piriya kōloḷkoṭṭa kariya nela
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Ī dharmmamanārorbbaraḷupidaḍe bāṇarāsiyoḷ sāvira kavileya (koṁda)
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> vāyō harēti vasundharā ṣaṣṭivaruṣa sahasrāṇi <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
